Silver nanoparticles (Ag NPs) were prepared by successive ionic layer adsorption and reaction (SILAR) method. The cationic precursor for Ag NPs using SILAR method was diammine silver complex Ag(NH3)2(aq)+\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
